                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5656" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1194</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10196 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">共享视像盛宴：海信并购整合TVS之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Sharing Visual Banquet: the Path of Hisense’s Acquisition and Integration of TVS</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">洪勇，李良玉，田琳玉</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大连理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">6 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">国际化；跨国并购；整合；2021百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Internationalization; Cross-border Merger and Acquisition; Integration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通过跨国并购实现国际化扩张，是过去一段时间中国企业参与全球竞争的一股重要潮流。案例介绍了中国家电企业海信对日本知名家电品牌东芝旗下TVS公司的收购与整合过程，从海信“未来发展‘大头在海外’”战略的提出、连续并购引发的质疑、海信对收购TVS的回应等方面再现了海信收购TVS事件的相关信息，从品牌并行发展、员工认同管理、市场渠道重构、技术互补利用等方面展示了海信收购TVS之后面临的形势及海信实施的整合措施。同时，也以全球销售情况、海外市场增长、公司经营业绩等方面的数据，展现了海信收购TVS至今的发展态势。希望通过对海信并购整合TVS案例的讨论与学习，学习者能深刻掌握企业跨国并购战略实施过程中的重要环节及关键要素。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">International expansion through cross-border mergers and acquisitions has been an important approach for Chinese enterprises to participate in global competition in the past few decades. Based on the background of Hisense’s acquisition and integration process of TVS, this case introduces the relevant details in the acquisition from a series of key points of the acquisition event, including the proposal of Hisense’s “‘counting on overseas markets’ for future growth” strategy, the direct challenge to the authority of continuous overseas mergers and acquisitions, and the response to the acquisition of TVS; and also displays the specific circumstances that Hisense needs to take into consideration after acquiring TVS, as well as a number of post-acquisition integration, which is often regarded as a complex set of organizational processes that ought to integrate the acquiring enterprise and the target enterprise from the perspectives of multiple development of brands, employees’ affective identification management, market channel reconstruction, complementary utilization of technologies and the forth. In the meanwhile, Hisense is maintaining a rapid development worldwide since the acquisition of TVS three years ago, which could be illustrated by a group of data specifically detailed in the global sales revenue, the overseas markets growth and the enterprise’s operating performance. Through a comprehensive discussion, it is expected that the significant relations and crucial factors in the implementation approach of enterprises’ cross-border merger and acquisition strategies could be better understood. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">跨国并购动因与并购整合等企业国际化并购战略管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-11</td>
                            </tr>
